  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: When the user is creating an account -right after creating a password- we are showing a screen with the text \"Creating your account on the blockchain. We can't touch it, no one can, except for you\". \r\n[This has been noted as inaccurate](https://status-im.slack.com/archives/C9R0TSTM2/p1531229410000482), so we decided to remove this screen directly.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nExpected sequence of screens during account creation:\r\n1- Initial screen\r\n2- Create password\r\n3- Confirm password\r\n4- Name\r\n5- Welcome screen\r\n\r\n![onboarding min - mobile copy 2](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/43403477-83c002be-93eb-11e8-91df-88e2d1705fa8.png)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nCurrent sequence of screens during account creation:\r\n1- Initial screen\r\n2- Create password\r\n3- Confirm password\r\n**3.1 - \"Creating your account on the blockchain...\" screen.**\r\n4- Name\r\n5- Welcome screen\r\n\r\n![onboarding min - mobile copy](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/43403405-58417d5c-93eb-11e8-9920-05b53ae8185f.png)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Select \"Other accounts\"\r\n- Select \"Create new account\"\r\n- Follow account creating steps\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\nRemove \"Creating your account on the blockchain....\" screen during account creation. **Add the \"Back\" button to the \"Name\" screen so it can follow the sequence.**\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\nChanges need to be implemented both on iOS and Android.\r\nOther changes on onboarding include:\r\n- Changing order of \"Name\" & \"Password\" screen #5336 \r\n- Other [copy changes](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/5089/files) by @obi2020 including \"Create account\" instead of \"Next\" on the button in the last screen.",
